<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Undead World - Homu</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./game.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="block" style="padding-left:20px">
    <h1>如何註冊</h1>
    1. 到綜合版回應討論串<br>
    2. 於E-mail輸入sage、內文輸入"我要出來玩"並輸入刪除密碼<br>
    3. 送出回應<br>
    4. 回到本頁填寫並送出表單<br>
    5. 伺服器將回應刪除並完成認證<br>
  </div>
  <br>
  <form class="VarifyForm block" action="./varify" method="POST">
    <div style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold;">註冊</div>
    <div><div class="VarifyFormText">ID</div><input type="text" name="id" class="VarifyFormInput"></div>
    <div><div class="VarifyFormText">討論串編號</div><input type="text" name="number" class="VarifyFormInput"></div>
    <div><div class="VarifyFormText">文章編號</div><input type="text" name="number" class="VarifyFormInput"></div>
    <div><div class="VarifyFormText">刪除用密碼</div><input type="text" name="password" class="VarifyFormInput"></div>
    <input type="Submit" value="Sing In" style="margin-top:5px;">
  </form>
</body>

</html>
